i can confirm that the volume edition (english) of office 2011 sp1 installs correctly.  I had a different torrent, but it ended up being a dud.

This one is good.  OP did good by uploading many different languages, allowing the user to pick 1.  I picked "dvd5 office 2011 standard w SP1 english" from the volume folder;  worked in osx 10.6.6.  make sure you do clean uninstall of any previous copies of office 2011 first:  http://mac2.microsoft.com/help/office/14/en-us/word/item/9e879258-ed91-43d0-94b8-002c3292fdc6   :D  will seed the one I quoted above on seedbox until maybe 50-100gb.
